Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything this world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the Grand Line\Nin pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:40.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:47.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:58.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.47,0:01:06.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:16.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:21.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:25.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:30.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:36.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:42.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:47.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:55.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've come all this way\Nafter crossing Aqua Laguna.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you think about it, it's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like they've at least got good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, we have permission to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy when we don't have to\Nworry about going easy on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drawbridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The Franky Family is\Ncurrently fighting to bring it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once it comes down, we can go\Nover to the other side at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... When it's right in front of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CP9...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I gave up everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want you to come to rescue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you come after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Everything Is for Her Friends!\NRobin in the Darkness!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna talk about Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did that woman change after\Nyou guys came to this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After she went out to town,\Nshe suddenly disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and by this morning, she was the\Nsuspect of your attempted assassination.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When my friends finally found her,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she said she would no longer come back to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't know what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:03:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we came here tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to ask her directly again\Nwhy she's leaving the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To make my wish come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wish that can never come true if I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this wish that can never\Ncome true if she's with us...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you what I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably when you lost sight\Nof Nico Robin the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CP9...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government's operation\Nwas already in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is, of course, a reason\Nfor that woman's actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before I tell you about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to know that Nico\NRobin and I both have a means
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to bring back the ancient weapon\Nthat could destroy the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A problem occurred in our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, come to the bedroom right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot Iceberg yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you get it, Nico Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The blueprints you guys were after are fakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I am to be killed, I won't give\Nthose blueprints to the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're sniffing around\Nthe Poneglyphs on another front
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and helping the Government as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I have to stop you right here, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not seeking the Poneglyphs\Nin order to bring the weapon back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to know the history, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a claim doesn't mean anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over... and over again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you don't intend to do so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons hurt people despite your intentions!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can even hurt those\Nwho mean a lot to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That which hurts people doesn't\Nnecessarily have malicious intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that simple curiosity of\Nwanting to know the history
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leads to the destruction of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should die right here,\Nright now, Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after you saw the Ohara devils' fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you still want to chase\Nafter the world's history?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like you know\Neverything about Ohara!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even know how much the\NWorld Government messed up my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hate the Government that much,\Nthen why are you helping them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have a wish I want to come true\Neven if I have to give up everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're two conditions that\NCP9 forced on me in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One is to pin the assassination\Non the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other is to turn myself in\Nto the Government and obey them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, you'll die, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you accept such conditions\Nafter evading them for 20 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this lone instance,\NCP9 has been given permission
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to exercise Buster Call against the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buster Call?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency order to\Nsummon five of the vice admirals
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from Navy Headquarters and\Nten battleships to one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've been targeted by the\Nnational war-class military power,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nothing will remain of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, in the Navy, this authority\Nonly belongs to the three admirals
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the head of the Navy, the fleet admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,through the admiral Aokiji,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CP9 was given the authority\Nto exercise it just this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't accept the conditions,\NBuster Call was going to be exercised on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard the name Aokiji, I gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always able to make good\Nmy escape for the past 20 years
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I had nothing to protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I could betray people\Nand use them as a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I really can't do that any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The life I once gave up on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heart that I lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dream I could no longer have...\NThey picked them all up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to make friends who\Nwould believe in someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, your wish is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:09:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That the six Straw Hats, excluding me,\Ncan leave this island safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying, for that, you don't\Ncare if the weapon is brought back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't care what happens to the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N... Nami! Are you there behind me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hey, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, that pigeon guy sent me flying
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I flew right into this gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fool around at a critical time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you've been taking your\Nsweet time, Robin was taken away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin intends to die for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She sacrificed herself in order to protect\Nus from an attack by the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she knew that she was going\Nto be killed if she was taken in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...after all, Robin was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoooa! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm warning you, this is a crazy train.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its name is Rocketman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:12:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't even allow passengers to be on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Well then, let's go, shall we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now departing Water Seven for Enies Lobby...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes the sea train Rocketman!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Depart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna go...! To get everything back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A power strong enough to give me control\Nover any large country I might desire
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is in my hands now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:14:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Aokiji give you the\Nauthority to exercise Buster Call?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in no position to ask me\Nquestions, you insolent woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't recognized\Nthe value of your existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would've been practically worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you should appreciate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, the repugnant kin of Ohara,\Nthe land of devils...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run to the evacuation ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Put out the fire!\N--Protect the books!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revealing the history isn't\Nwhat Ohara was trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just wanted to accept the voices\Nof the past and protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'll stay here, too! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alone now, but you'll\Nmeet friends someday for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The sea is vast, so someday, definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll come across friends who'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Monster!\N--Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her mom abandoned her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is born into this world to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will understand someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that she's a survivor\Nof those Ohara devils
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who planned the world's annihilation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let her get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, give me the money!\NI reported her to you, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sin is being alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go meet the friends who're\Nsurely waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,somewhere at sea, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sogeking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot through that flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my new weapon,\Na huge slingshot... named Kabuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good look at its power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack... Firebird Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you insane?! Don't think\Nthat you'll be able to survive
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after making the entire world your enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still haven't heard you say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say you want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To live...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be allowed\Nto live in this world, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your existence itself is a huge crime, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was something I dared not wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one ever let me wish for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is vast, so someday, definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll come across friends who'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If... it's really okay for me\Nto utter my wish for once...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to the sea with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the assassin group CP9 on my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cutty Flam...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Straw Hat Theater"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Part 5"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rodusa is wearing sunglasses because\Nshe's a monster known as the Gorgon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who turns people to stone\Nwhen they look her in the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she didn't have eye contact with\Nanyone today for a different reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Dragon. Give me those mystical horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always shooting at me.\NIt hurts, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:50.62,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a monster, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:53.10,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Centaur\NUsoppaka"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:53.29,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dragon\NLugyao"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:55.42,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got time, why don't you fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:58.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystical fish live in this sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:21:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I want the mystical horns, not mystical fish.\N--This is a village called\NMonston in a monster forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Like I said, catch some fish.\N--I'm gonna make bugle horns out of them.\N--where monsters live free from care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you have a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.65,0:21:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:11.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! I got tricked by the sweet bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:13.81,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kraken (Giant Octopus)\NChoperken"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:16.90,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,You again, Choperken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing on the sea floor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for a mystical treasure\Nthat's on the sea floor right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, give me\Nmore of those sweet baits!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:29.57,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Choperken!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:30.37,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mermaid\NStronamie"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:33.79,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lay your hands on that\Nmystical treasure, you'll pay for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's laying on the sea floor,\Nso first come, first served.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You've got some nerve.\NYou wanna compete with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Scary!\N--Hiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:42.92,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,What idiot is troubling my love, Stronamie-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:46.58,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Water Imp\NSanzaler"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:51.48,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna beat him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what're you doing?\NAre you trying to catch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mystical fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:21:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a fish! I'm a water imp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More like a naughty monster who lives\Nin the sea despite being a water imp.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:01.77,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Give yourself up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.79,0:22:02.28,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Minotaur\NZoromilk"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:05.28,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?! You're a minotaur,\Nand yet you're a Holstein!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:09.45,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. I'm gonna get that mystical\Nbowl on your head today for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let you have it.\NIt'll endanger my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, I heard that that\Niron rod you have is a mystical thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try and get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystical this, mystical that...\NYou guys are all mystical beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gasp!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.66,0:22:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know, Rodusa.\NYou were crying the other day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.20,0:22:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,saying that you lost your mystical earrings,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we decided to give\Nsomething even rarer to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! Don't spill the beans!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why she doesn't\Nlook in everyone's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.51,0:22:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is in order to hide her happiness,\Nembarrassment, and tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.77,0:22:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.29,0:22:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:23:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is Monston,\Na village of carefree monsters.\N--Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! Sorry to have kept you waiting!\NI'm coming for you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.83,0:23:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The pirates are coming here!\NWe have to go to the Gates of Justice now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.71,0:23:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cutty Flam...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.38,0:23:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... What you have in your hand is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hand those blueprints over to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.55,0:23:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm Not Gonna Hand over\Nthe Blueprints! Franky's Decision"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.60,0:23:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
